Package: FlexBayesMed
Type: Package
Title: Modeling Skewed and Heavy-Tailed Errors in Bayesian Mediation Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Zongyu", "Li",
           email = "zli37@nd.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Zongyu Li <zli37@nd.edu>
Description: Flexible Bayesian mediation models, including simulation from
    the centered two-piece t-distribution (CTPT). Provides methods
    for skewed and heavy-tailed error modeling in a mediation framework.
